  The games.eclass has dropped GAMES_CHECK_LICENSE support (since portage now
  has ACCEPT_LICENSE), so drop it here too.

  17 Nov 2011; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Change developer's email

